OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773065474
OL,3,CFamily's warning three years after mum
OL,4,Ckilled by drink-driver
OL,6,FThe family of a popular lollipop lady
OL,7,Ffrom Yate who was killed by a drink-
OL,8,Fdriver have said they continue to live
OL,9,Fin a "nightmare" after losing her.
OL,11,FRebecca Ashmead, known to her loved
OL,12,Fones as Bex, was on her way to spend
OL,13,Fthe evening with her son Fen in March
OL,14,F2023 when she was hit by a car near
OL,15,Fher South Gloucestershire home.
OL,17,FShe was killed by Ashley Billing, a 40-
OL,18,Fyear-old man who had been driving
OL,19,Fwhile banned, under the influence of
OL,20,Falcohol. He has since been jailed for
OL,21,Fnine years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
