PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773065474
OL,3,CFamily's warning three years after mum
OL,4,Ckilled by drink-driver
OL,6,FBex's family were taking part in Avon
OL,7,Fand Somerset Police's campaign to to
OL,8,Fstop dangerous driving on roads in the
OL,9,Fforce area.
OL,11,FAccording to latest figures, every
OL,12,Fday, two people are either killed or
OL,13,Finjured in car crashes in the force's
OL,14,Farea.
OL,16,FThe force is now highlighting what it
OL,17,Fcalls the fatal five causes of road
OL,18,Fcrashes: motorists not wearing
OL,19,Fseatbelts, driving carelessly,
OL,20,Fspeeding, using mobile phones and
OL,21,Ftaking drugs or alcohol.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773065474
OL,3,CFamily's warning three years after mum
OL,4,Ckilled by drink-driver
OL,6,FSpeaking about the family's grief,
OL,7,FRebcca's son Fen Trudgian said: "For
OL,8,Fas long as I can remember, my biggest
OL,9,Ffear was losing my mum, since I was a
OL,10,Flittle kid.
OL,12,F"It is impossible to put into words
OL,13,Fthe effect that it has. When you have
OL,14,Fthe one person who is ever-present in
OL,15,Fyour life, shouting the loudest, the
OL,16,Fbiggest voice in the room, it is
OL,17,Fimpossible to live without that, once
OL,18,Fyou've experienced it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773065474
OL,3,CFamily's warning three years after mum
OL,4,Ckilled by drink-driver
OL,6,F"When I go back to that day, it's
OL,7,Fprobably the most visceral memory. I
OL,8,Fthink it's going to be with me
OL,9,Fforever. On the one hand, I love to
OL,10,Fremember that my mum was on her way
OL,11,Finto Bristol, on her way to come and
OL,12,Fsee me after work. We were going to go
OL,13,Fand spend the evening together.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773065474
OL,3,CFamily's warning three years after mum
OL,4,Ckilled by drink-driver
OL,6,F"I know she would have been excited
OL,7,Fand happy and I was too. But the way
OL,8,Fthat things played out and the way
OL,9,Fthat evening descended from excitement
OL,10,Ffor a fun plan into the eventual
OL,11,Frealisation when I arrived home,
OL,12,Fgreeted by my two sisters at the door
OL,13,Fand being told the worst news I could
OL,14,Fever receive.
OL,16,F"It hits me in my gut and I can't ever
OL,17,Fforget how that felt. The pain I felt
OL,18,Fin my heart and the scream that came
OL,19,Fout of me. I can hear that in my head
OL,20,Fwhenever I think about that day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773065474
OL,3,CFamily's warning three years after mum
OL,4,Ckilled by drink-driver
OL,6,F"We were robbed of the ability to say
OL,7,Fgoodbye and have any closure. I will
OL,8,Fnever come to terms with that."
OL,10,FCaroline Court, Rebecca's sister has
OL,11,Fremembered her as a 'key member of the
OL,12,Fcommunity' in her role as lollipop
OL,13,Flady as well as fundraiser and
OL,14,Ffriendly face.
OL,16,F"Bex was the hardest working person
OL,17,FI've ever known. She wanted to do
OL,18,Feverything for everyone and give her
OL,19,Fkids every opportunity. She was very
OL,20,Ffamily-oriented. She had so much zest
OL,21,Ffor life, energy and boundless love."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773065474
OL,3,CFamily's warning three years after mum
OL,4,Ckilled by drink-driver
OL,6,F"The anger that comes with the grief
OL,7,Fis palpable for me, every day still.
OL,8,FIt feels like it's just been a moment.
OL,9,FIt still doesn't feel real because we
OL,10,Fare continuing to go through
OL,11,Fmilestones that are getting missed all
OL,12,Fthe time. Our person is missing."
OL,14,FTae Ashmead, Bex's daughter, who was
OL,15,Fliving with her mum at the time of the
OL,16,Ftragedy said: "She brought so much joy
OL,17,Fand happiness. She was our biggest
OL,18,Fcheerleader. She was the loudest in
OL,19,Fthe room and always supporting us.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773065474
OL,3,CFamily's warning three years after mum
OL,4,Ckilled by drink-driver
OL,6,F"I remember when it first happened,
OL,7,Fgoing to sleep that night. It didn't
OL,8,Ffeel like that was our life. It felt
OL,9,Flike we were living in a nightmare
OL,10,Ffilm. I couldn't sleep for weeks. It
OL,11,Fhappened so close to our house as
OL,12,Fwell. Everything just felt really
OL,13,Fwrong."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
